Pavitra Gyaan — Next.js + OpenAI demo

Steps to deploy:
1. Push this repo to GitHub.
2. Go to https://vercel.com → Import Project → select this GitHub repo.
3. In Vercel Project Settings → Environment Variables, add:
   - Key: OPENAI_API_KEY
   - Value: <your OpenAI API key>
4. Deploy. Visit homepage and test.

Note: This implementation uses OpenAI to generate text. For higher astrological precision use Swiss Ephemeris calculations on a backend (Python with pyswisseph).
